>143</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>12/8/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>2:59:49 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/TimesSquare/Labyrinth/1868/Ed.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">FYI regarding KoP in Hate on Monday</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">The Knights of Phoenix has invited Council of Friends to join them in their Hate raid on Monday.  The reason for bringing this to your attention is that there will be 7 CoF.  Being that CoF is not a posting entity, we figured that it would be acceptable to the Rathe community.  If it is not, please let me know.<br>
